        "duration": "Permanent",
        "range": "30'",
        "roll": "",
        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: Permanent</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 30'</strong></p>\n<p>Conjures food from thin air.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Volume: </strong>Food sufficient for twelve humans and twelve mounts for one day is conjured.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Higher level casters: </strong>If the caster is higher than 8th level, food sufficient for an additional 12 humans and mounts is produced for each level beyond 8th.</p>",
