      "img": "systems/wwn/assets/default/spell.png",
      "effects": [],
      "system": {
        "lvl": 5,
        "class": "Cleric",
        "duration": "up to 1 day",
        "range": "480'",
        "roll": "",
        "description": "<p><strong>Duration: Concentration (up to 1 day)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Range: 480&rsquo;</strong></p>\n<p>Cast above ground, this spell conjures a 60&rsquo; diameter swarm of flying insects with the following properties:</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Movement: </strong>20&rsquo; per round. While the swarm is within range, the caster is able to direct its movements.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Vision: </strong>Within the area of the swarm is obscured.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Creatures of 2 HD or less: </strong>Are driven away, if caught within the swarm.</p>\n<p><strong>▶ Concentration:</strong> If the caster moves or loses concentration, the swarm dissipates, ending the spell.</p>\n<p><strong>Restrictions: </strong>The spell has no effect if&nbsp;cast underground.</p>",
        "prepared": true,
        "cast": 0,
